	<li> Optional: A Brief Bio </li>
      </ul>
      
      <br>
      
      <p> Submit your proposal to <b> carolinacon[at]protonmail[dot]com </b> </p>
      <p> Please include "CarolinaCon15 - Call For Papers" in the subject line </p>
      <p> Presenters will receive: </p>
      <ul>
	<li> Free CarolinaCon admission for you and one (1) guest </li>
